  "bodyText": "Short, hands-on training courses in trades, creative work and wellness, run two sessions a week at community centres across Barbados.\n\n## Overview\n\nPractical demand-driven skill training in 25+ courses across trades, creative services, and wellness. Two sessions/week, 2-3 hours, morning/midday/afternoon/evening slots at community and resource centres island-wide.\n\n## Who can apply\n\n- 16+ years\n- Interest in trades, wellness, creative, community, training\n\n## How to apply\n\nComplete the short application form to register your interest. Your progress is saved automatically.\n\n<!-- [Apply now](https://alpha.gov.bb/youth-and-community/skills-trades-vocational-training/cip/form) -->\n\n## More information\n\n[Go to the official site for Community Impact Programme (CIP)](https://comdev.gov.bb/programmes/cip/)"
